==German==

===Noun===
'''Rechtsschutzversicherungsgesellschaften'''
# [[insurance]] [[companies]] which provide [[legal]] [[protection]].

====Trivia====
This word is the longest German word in everyday use, according to the Guiness Book of World Records, with 39 characters ([http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Donaudampfschiffahrtselektrizit%C3%A4tenhauptbetriebswerkbauunterbeamtengesellschaft].